      <t>A Layer 2 Gateway (L2GW) is used for interconnecting a Layer 2 overlay network [NVO3FRWK] and a Layer 2 bridged network [IEEE802.1Q] to form a single Layer 2 virtual network. This draft describes data plane interconnection and control plane interworking at the L2GW.</t>
